data-triple-N3.o: "Portsmouth Football Club is a professional football club based in the city of Portsmouth, England. Portsmouth's home matches have been played at Fratton Park since the club's formation in 1898. The club is playing in Football League One, the third tier in the English football league system, in the 2012–13 season after being relegated from the Football League Championship in 2011–12."@en
